@page "/"

<PageTitle>Maasi | Personal Website</PageTitle>

<section class="hero" aria-labelledby="home-heading">
    <div class="hero-content">
        <p class="eyebrow">Personal website</p>
        <h1 id="home-heading">Maasi</h1>
        <p class="hero-copy">
            I am building my own corner of the web with Blazor: a place for what I am working on,
            where to find me, and the recipes I keep coming back to.
        </p>

        <div class="hero-actions" aria-label="Primary links">
            <a class="action primary" href="recipes">View recipes</a>
            <a class="action secondary" href="mailto:hello@example.com">Say hello</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="content-band about-band" aria-labelledby="doing-heading">
    <div class="section-heading">
        <p class="eyebrow">Now</p>
        <h2 id="doing-heading">What I am doing</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="focus-grid">
        <article class="focus-item">
            <span class="focus-kicker">Learning</span>
            <h3>Building with Blazor</h3>
            <p>Practicing C#, Razor components, layouts, routing, and clean front-end structure.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="focus-item">
            <span class="focus-kicker">Creating</span>
            <h3>Growing a personal site</h3>
            <p>Turning this into a portfolio-style home with projects, updates, and useful links.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="focus-item">
            <span class="focus-kicker">Cooking</span>
            <h3>Collecting recipes</h3>
            <p>Keeping favorite meals in one place so they are easy to revisit and share.</p>
        </article>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="content-band split-band" aria-labelledby="connect-heading">
    <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Connect</p>
        <h2 id="connect-heading">Find me around the internet</h2>
        <p>
            A few places for projects, updates, photos, and a direct hello.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="social-list" aria-label="Social links">
        <a href="https://github.com/your-username" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/your-username" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/your-username" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Instagram</a>
        <a href="mailto:hello@example.com">Email</a>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="content-band recipe-callout" aria-labelledby="recipe-heading">
    <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Recipes</p>
        <h2 id="recipe-heading">A small kitchen notebook</h2>
        <p>
            A few everyday meals with ingredients, timing, and steps kept together.
        </p>
    </div>

    <a class="action primary" href="recipes">Open recipes</a>
</section>
